<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Mentor Application Update – Graphora</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0f0f0f;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #1a1a1a;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1 0%, #4f46e5 100%);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 26px;
        }

        .header p {
            margin: 8px 0 0;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
            font-size: 15px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 36px 32px;
            color: #e0e0e0;
        }

        .content h2 {
            color: #fff;
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .reason-box {
            background: #242424;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px 24px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
        }

        .reason-box p.label {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: #f59e0b;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .reason-box p.text {
            margin: 0;
            color: #ccc;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .encouragement {
            background: #1e2a1e;
            border: 1px solid #2d4a2d;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .encouragement p {
            margin: 0 0 8px;
            color: #86efac;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .encouragement ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #a0c4a0;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .encouragement li {
            margin: 4px 0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: block;
            width: fit-content;
            margin: 24px auto;
            padding: 14px 36px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #6366f1, #4f46e5);
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #111;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #555;
            border-top: 1px solid #222;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #6366f1;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Application Update</h1>
            <p>We've reviewed your mentor application</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi {{mentorName}},</h2>
            <p>Thank you for your interest in becoming a Graphora mentor. After careful review, we're unable to approve
                your application at this time.</p>

            <div class="reason-box">
                <p class="label">📋 Feedback:</p>
                <p class="text">{{reason}}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="encouragement">
                <p>💡 You can reapply! Here's how to strengthen your application:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Add more detail about your industry experience</li>
                    <li>Highlight specific technologies and companies</li>
                    <li>Include a LinkedIn profile for verification</li>
                    <li>Describe the type of sessions you want to offer</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>We encourage you to update your profile and reapply. Many successful mentors were approved on their
                second
                attempt.</p>

            <a href="{{reapplyUrl}}" class="btn">Update & Reapply</a>

            <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #666; text-align: center;">Questions? Our team is happy to provide
                feedback.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Need help? <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>© 2025 Graphora. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>